IMAGiNE bringing you another release.....Robin Hood

Well many thanks to the spanish grp that released this video and also many thanks to Lu
for the audio
Right work done......fixed up the colours to make it look a bit more natural and also balanced out
the rgb colours a touch,personally though there was too much red to start with.
Also made it a touch sharper and fix the AR ....along with a few other tweaks.
Audio .....we just stripped Lu's and remuxed over this video ....so thanks for the sync aswell bro

Right as or sources .....yes it's not the best video around thats for sure and yes there is better coming
very soon,but for now this is the best source out so .
File size is bigger than the other encodes due to the fact we kept the same bitrate as the source file as
lowering it would only make it worse than it already is so...
Audio,not too bad for a cam got to say.....defo heard alot worse than this.

So basically guys if you can wait then wait ....if not grab this for now and enjoy
